#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:1
msgid "Configure grid map environment"
msgstr "配置网格地图环境"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:4
msgid ""
"The grid map is a 2D occupancy grid used for collision detection and path "
"planning. You configure it via the **``obstacle_map``** key in the "
"``world`` section of the YAML file. The grid is built by a **map "
"generator**; built-in generators are **image** (from a PNG file) and "
"**perlin** (procedural noise). You can also add custom generators (see "
"[Adding a new map generator](#add-new-map-generator))."
msgstr ""
"网格地图是用于碰撞检测和路径规划的二维占据栅格。通过 YAML 文件 ``world`` 部分的 "
"**``obstacle_map``** 键进行配置。栅格由 **地图生成器** 构建；内置生成器有 "
"**image**（来自 PNG 文件）和 **perlin**（程序化噪声）。也可添加自定义生成器"
"（参见[添加新地图生成器](#add-new-map-generator)）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:7
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:10
msgid ""
"- **``obstacle_map``** accepts: **``null``**, a **generator spec dict** "
"(recommended), a **string path** (shorthand for image), or an "
"**ndarray** (programmatic use only)."
msgstr ""
"- **``obstacle_map``** 接受：**``null``**、**生成器配置字典**（推荐）、"
"**字符串路径**（图像的简写形式）或 **ndarray**（仅限程序化使用）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:11
msgid ""
"- **Generator spec** is a dict with ``name`` identifying the generator "
"and generator-specific parameters. Grid size and semantics depend on the "
"generator."
msgstr ""
"- **生成器配置** 是一个字典，``name`` 标识生成器，其余为生成器特定参数。"
"栅格大小和语义取决于所用生成器。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:12
msgid ""
"- **``mdownsample``** (world section): downsampling factor applied to "
"the generated grid to reduce resolution and computation."
msgstr ""
"- **``mdownsample``**（world 部分）：对生成的栅格进行降采样的因子，"
"用于降低分辨率和计算量。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:15
msgid "Quick example"
msgstr "快速示例"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md
msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md
msgid "YAML (image map)"
msgstr "YAML（图像地图）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md
msgid "Demonstration"
msgstr "演示"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:84
msgid "Obstacle map types"
msgstr "障碍物地图类型"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:87
msgid "**Canonical form: generator spec dict**"
msgstr "**标准形式：生成器配置字典**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:89
msgid ""
"Use a dict with ``name`` and parameters. Two built-in generators:"
msgstr ""
"使用包含 ``name`` 和参数的字典。两个内置生成器："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:91
msgid ""
"- **``name: image``** — load grid from an image file. Only ``path`` is "
"required. Grid size comes from the image dimensions."
msgstr ""
"- **``name: image``** — 从图像文件加载栅格。仅需 ``path`` 参数。"
"栅格大小来源于图像尺寸。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:92
msgid ""
"- **``name: perlin``** — procedural Perlin noise grid. Requires "
"``resolution`` (meters per cell); grid size = world ``width`` / "
"``height`` ÷ ``resolution``."
msgstr ""
"- **``name: perlin``** — 程序化 Perlin 噪声栅格。需要 ``resolution``（每格米数）；"
"栅格大小 = 世界 ``width`` / ``height`` ÷ ``resolution``。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:94
msgid "**Other accepted values**"
msgstr "**其他可接受的值**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:96
msgid ""
"- **String** (e.g. ``'cave.png'``): treated as ``{ name: image, path: "
"'cave.png' }`` (backward compatible)."
msgstr ""
"- **字符串**（如 ``'cave.png'``）：视为 ``{ name: image, path: 'cave.png' }``"
"（向后兼容）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:97
msgid "- **``null``**: no obstacle map (empty free space)."
msgstr "- **``null``**：无障碍物地图（空白可通行空间）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:98
msgid ""
"- **ndarray**: programmatic use only (e.g. when constructing the world "
"in Python). Float array 0–100; cells above 50 are obstacles. Not "
"available from YAML."
msgstr ""
"- **ndarray**：仅限程序化使用（如在 Python 中构建世界时）。浮点数组 0–100；"
"大于 50 的格为障碍物。不可从 YAML 使用。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:101
msgid "Built-in generators"
msgstr "内置生成器"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:104
msgid "Image generator (``name: image``)"
msgstr "图像生成器（``name: image``）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:106
msgid ""
"Loads an image file (e.g. PNG) and converts it to a 0–100 occupancy "
"grid. Black pixels become obstacles (high value), white pixels free "
"space (low value). Grid size is the image size in pixels."
msgstr ""
"加载图像文件（如 PNG）并将其转换为 0–100 占据栅格。黑色像素为障碍物（高值），"
"白色像素为可通行空间（低值）。栅格大小为图像的像素尺寸。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:108
msgid "**YAML (explicit):**"
msgstr "**YAML（显式）：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:120
msgid ""
"**YAML (shorthand):** ``obstacle_map: 'cave.png'`` is equivalent to "
"the above."
msgstr "**YAML（简写）：** ``obstacle_map: 'cave.png'`` 等同于上述配置。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:122
msgid ""
"**Image location:** The path is resolved relative to the script "
"directory or the package ``world/map`` search path. You can use "
"absolute or relative paths. Place ``cave.png`` in the same directory "
"as your script, or set the path accordingly."
msgstr ""
"**图像位置：** 路径相对于脚本目录或包内 ``world/map`` 搜索路径解析。"
"可使用绝对或相对路径。将 ``cave.png`` 放在脚本同目录下，或相应设置路径。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:130
msgid ""
"Use custom PNG images for different environments. Values are "
"interpreted as: darker → obstacle, lighter → free. Absolute or "
"relative paths are supported."
msgstr ""
"使用自定义 PNG 图像可创建不同环境。值的解释为：越暗 → 障碍物，越亮 → 可通行。"
"支持绝对和相对路径。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:135
msgid "Perlin generator (``name: perlin``)"
msgstr "Perlin 生成器（``name: perlin``）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:137
msgid ""
"Procedural grid from Perlin noise. Grid size is determined by world "
"size and ``resolution``: e.g. world 20 m × 20 m with "
"``resolution: 0.1`` gives 200×200 cells."
msgstr ""
"由 Perlin 噪声生成的程序化栅格。栅格大小由世界尺寸和 ``resolution`` 决定："
"例如 20 m × 20 m 的世界配合 ``resolution: 0.1`` 可得 200×200 格。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:156
msgid ""
"**Parameters** (see ``irsim.world.map.PerlinGridGenerator``): "
"``complexity``, ``fill``, ``fractal``, ``attenuation``, ``seed`` "
"(optional). ``resolution`` is required; ``width`` and ``height`` (in "
"cells) are computed from world size and must not be set in YAML."
msgstr ""
"**参数**（参见 ``irsim.world.map.PerlinGridGenerator``）："
"``complexity``、``fill``、``fractal``、``attenuation``、``seed``"
"（可选）。``resolution`` 为必需；``width`` 和 ``height``（格数）"
"由世界尺寸计算，不可在 YAML 中设置。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:158
msgid ""
"Full example: ``usage/10grid_map/grid_map_perlin.yaml`` and "
"``grid_map_perlin.py``."
msgstr "完整示例：``usage/10grid_map/grid_map_perlin.yaml`` 和 ``grid_map_perlin.py``。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:161
msgid "Downsampling (``mdownsample``)"
msgstr "降采样（``mdownsample``）"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:164
msgid ""
"``mdownsample`` is an integer (default 1) applied to the generated "
"grid: the grid is subsampled by this factor (e.g. 2 → every 2×2 block "
"becomes one cell). Use it to reduce resolution and speed up collision "
"checks. Only applies when an obstacle map is present."
msgstr ""
"``mdownsample`` 是一个整数（默认 1），作用于生成的栅格：按此因子对栅格降采样"
"（如 2 → 每 2×2 块合并为一格）。用于降低分辨率并加速碰撞检测。"
"仅在存在障碍物地图时生效。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:167
msgid "Adding a new map generator"
msgstr "添加新地图生成器"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:171
msgid ""
"To add a custom generator (e.g. maze, other procedural maps), implement "
"a class under **``irsim/world/map/``** and register it by importing in "
"**``irsim/world/map/__init__.py``**."
msgstr ""
"要添加自定义生成器（如迷宫或其他程序化地图），在 **``irsim/world/map/``** 下实现一个类，"
"并在 **``irsim/world/map/__init__.py``** 中导入以完成注册。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:173
msgid "**1. Implement the generator**"
msgstr "**1. 实现生成器**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:175
msgid ""
"- Subclass **``GridMapGenerator``** (from "
"``irsim.world.map.grid_map_generator_base``)."
msgstr ""
"- 继承 **``GridMapGenerator``**（来自 "
"``irsim.world.map.grid_map_generator_base``）。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:176
msgid ""
"- Implement **``_build_grid(self) -> np.ndarray``**: return an occupancy "
"grid of shape ``(width, height)``, values 0–100 (values > 50 are "
"obstacles). The framework passes ``width`` and ``height`` to your "
"``__init__`` (derived from world size and ``resolution``)."
msgstr ""
"- 实现 **``_build_grid(self) -> np.ndarray``**：返回形状为 ``(width, height)`` 的"
"占据栅格，值 0–100（> 50 为障碍物）。框架会将 ``width`` 和 ``height``"
"（由世界尺寸和 ``resolution`` 计算）传递给 ``__init__``。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:177
msgid "- Set class attributes:"
msgstr "- 设置类属性："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:178
msgid "- **``name``** (str): YAML key, e.g. ``name = \"maze\"``."
msgstr "- **``name``**（str）：YAML 键名，如 ``name = \"maze\"``。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:179
msgid ""
"- **``yaml_param_names``** (tuple): parameter names from YAML passed to "
"``__init__`` (e.g. ``(\"seed\", \"density\")``). Do **not** include "
"``\"name\"``, ``\"resolution\"``, ``\"width\"``, or ``\"height\"`` — "
"``resolution`` is required in the spec; ``width`` and ``height`` are "
"injected by the framework."
msgstr ""
"- **``yaml_param_names``**（tuple）：从 YAML 传递给 ``__init__`` 的参数名"
"（如 ``(\"seed\", \"density\")``）。**不要** 包含 ``\"name\"``、``\"resolution\"``、"
"``\"width\"`` 或 ``\"height\"`` — ``resolution`` 在配置中为必需项；"
"``width`` 和 ``height`` 由框架注入。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:181
msgid "**2. Register**"
msgstr "**2. 注册**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:183
msgid ""
"Import the new class in **``irsim/world/map/__init__.py``**. Registration "
"is automatic: subclasses of ``GridMapGenerator`` with a non-empty "
"``name`` are added to ``GridMapGenerator.registry`` when the class is "
"defined. Optionally add the class to ``__all__``."
msgstr ""
"在 **``irsim/world/map/__init__.py``** 中导入新类。注册是自动的："
"``GridMapGenerator`` 的子类在定义时，若 ``name`` 非空则自动添加到 "
"``GridMapGenerator.registry``。可选择将其加入 ``__all__``。"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:185
msgid "**3. Use in YAML**"
msgstr "**3. 在 YAML 中使用**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:187
msgid ""
"Your generator (like ``perlin``) goes through "
"``build_grid_from_generator``: the spec must include ``name`` and "
"``resolution``. Grid size is (world width / resolution, world height / "
"resolution). Example:"
msgstr ""
"自定义生成器（如 ``perlin``）通过 ``build_grid_from_generator`` 处理："
"配置中必须包含 ``name`` 和 ``resolution``。栅格大小为"
"（世界宽度 / resolution，世界高度 / resolution）。示例："

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:200
msgid "**Skeleton example:**"
msgstr "**框架示例：**"

#: ../../source/usage/configure_grid_map.md:224
msgid ""
"**Note:** The **``image``** generator is special: it does not use "
"``resolution`` or world size (grid comes from the image) and is handled "
"in ``resolve_obstacle_map``. All other generators use "
"``build_grid_from_generator`` and require ``resolution``; ``width`` and "
"``height`` are computed and passed by the framework."
msgstr ""
"**注意：** **``image``** 生成器较为特殊：它不使用 ``resolution`` 或世界尺寸"
"（栅格来源于图像），由 ``resolve_obstacle_map`` 处理。所有其他生成器均使用 "
"``build_grid_from_generator`` 且需要 ``resolution``；``width`` 和 ``height`` "
"由框架计算并传入。"
